title: #92Noon in Duluth! Shuster/Randolph/Zimmer Presser!
description: #92Noon is LIVE at Clyde Iron Works in Duluth! Olympic Gold Medalist John Shuster joins the program, Duluth East Greyhounds Boys Hockey Head Coach Mike Randolph talks puck, and Mike Zimmer addresses the media at the end of the 2018 Vikings Mini Camp!
